name: CD - A PROSPECT OF DESPAIR (free delivery)
description:
10 song album with brutal beatdowns and fast thrashing riffs.

1. The Entrance to Despair (intro)
2. Create to Destroy
3. A Sign of Absence
4. Closure
5. Facing faded Solutions
6. Through the Hourglass
7. Numb
8. Hope Dies Last
9. Unseen Sight
10. Drowning in Agony
11. Tradition of Ignorance

DRAIN LIFE  have been around for 13 years now and have released 2 eps prior to this full length cd. If there was a premier league of Dutch moshcore these guys would have been champions for years !!!
Aggression and brutality go hand in hand layered with venomous lyrics that will bring you nightmares about the apocalypse! There will be no quarter when Drain Life enters a stage and starts pumping out their soundtrack for violence (and fun!).  These guys will keep you moshing for many more years...
 
For fans of: Merauder, Hatebreed, Lamb of God and Heaven shall burn !
